HEADWORD: By-bidder
<hw>By"-bid`der</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who bids at
an auction in behalf of the auctioneer or owner, for the purpose of
running up the price of articles.</def> <mark>[U.S.]</mark><-- a type of
<altname>shill</altname> -->⟦br⟧
